original_title: ONE Friday Fights 10: Yodkrisada vs. Thepthaksin
overview: ONE Friday Fights 10: Yodkrisada vs. Thepthaksin (also known as ONE Lumpinee 10) was a combat sports event produced by ONE Championship that took place on March 24, 2023, at Lumpinee Boxing Stadium in Bangkok, Thailand.
title: ONE Friday Fights 10: Yodkrisada vs. Thepthaksin
